title: Echoveil - Infinite Paper Sky (2014) [Instrumental Metal] [Mp3 3
description:
Heavy rhythms, harmonic leads, and tasty solos! This is my first metal release in over six years. I've put a lot of time and effort into this release, so I hope you enjoy listening to it as much as I enjoyed making it. Please spread the word!


If you'd rather have FLAC or uncompressed, you can head over to my bandcamp at:

echoveil . bandcamp . com

or links are available from:

echoveil . com


If you enjoy the music, the bandcamp has an option to pay for the album, if you wish to support me and help me make the next one!



Influences:

Protest the Hero, Cloudkicker, The Black Dahlia Murder, (early) In Flames, Secret & Whisper, Saosin, Russian Circles
